This repo have MVVM Design Pattern exercise applications which ones have combined with different APIs. 

Exercise 1 is a basic API data windowing application, 
Exercise 2 is a Web API based get and post cabailities application, 
Exercise 3 is a basic weather app which one is connected with openweatherAPI.
Exercise 4 is a really basic application, it has include API, MVVM Design Pattern and Binding application. 

Binding folder; this folder has include binding exercise and explains how it works and what is the main idea of binding.

All applications have detailed turkish explains for what I did, how I did and why I did inside. 
